\begin{abstract}
  This project aims to develop an interactive and educational chatbot
  application for the \naosix\ humanoid robot, enhancing its
  capabilities through Large Language Model (LLM) integration. Hosted by
  the Computer Science Department at Indiana University South Bend, the
  \naosix\ robot will leverage advanced AI to engage users in meaningful
  conversations while performing interactive animations.
\end{abstract}

\begin{IEEEkeywords}
  \naosix, NAO6, humanoid robot, LLM, Ollama, Docker.
\end{IEEEkeywords}
